1. *Blago* nam onima koji nisu zaboravili našu prošlost. (Blessings to those who have not forgotten our past.)
2. On je bio naivni dečak, ali je dobio *blago*.  (He was a naive boy, but he got a blessing.)
3. *Blago* vam svim koji su pomogli u ovom projektu. (Blessings to all of you who helped in this project.)
4. Njegov otac mu je ostavio *blago*. (His father left him a blessing.)
5. Ona je dala *blago* svojoj porodici. (She gave a blessing to her family.)